  introLines:
  - Abra-ca... wait, where are my flash cotton sparks?
  - For my next trick, I will make myself vanish from this courtroom! ...Did it work?
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: The children in the front row were heckling me. I decided
    to pull out the grand finale early, got distracted by a kid throwing popcorn,
    and choked
  answerWhatKindOfLife: A life of pure illusion and wonder! I brought magic to the
    masses, even if the magic was just cheap smoke bombs and mirrors
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I am a Master of the Dark Arts! Or, according to my tax returns,
    a freelance entertainer for children's birthday parties
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: A true sorcerer never explains his wardrobe. Let's just
    say a smoke bomb detonated a little too close to my shirt
  answerWhyHaveItem: This witch hat channels my mystical energies. Without it, I'm
    just a regular guy in a wrinkled shirt. We can't have that
